{"TopicId":212160,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Color manager","CreatedByName":"FreeSpaceIndustry","CreatedById":161422,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T07:56:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"FreeSpaceIndustry","CreatedById":161422,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T07:56:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, a started this topic to talk about the color manager. (Love the concept and happy to see it in KSP 2)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I was able to gather from the available videos, is that you can select 2 colors as the agency colors, also change them on parts or on the assembly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I did not see was the option to save different color pairs as presets. I would really like the option to color code my missions or my sub\u00A0 assemblies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022198.71\u0022 height=\u0022773\u0022 width=\u0022389\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/7JHGFfM/image.png\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdding a list option where you can select presets, a string input filed where you can name a preset and a save/delete button should fit into the above editor easily.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA input field for hex or RGB color codes would also be nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOpinions?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sumghai","CreatedById":66272,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T09:42:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI concur with all of the above, especially the ability to enter hex / RGB color codes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would also be nice to be able to save and retrieve multiple presets, beyond the two Agency Colors.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T16:33:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd matte paint!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"whatsEJstandfor","CreatedById":220814,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T02:21:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236504\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221676997181\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd matte paint!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcuse me, it\u0027s spelled Matt Lowne\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astr0Guy5","CreatedById":225367,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T05:04:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236179\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221676966187\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161422\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FreeSpaceIndustry\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, FreeSpaceIndustry said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA input field for hex or RGB color codes would also be nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m pretty sure this was confirmed to be a feature added later in development (confirmed by Lowne I think?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomething that would make for more unique ships is more variety in paint jobs.\u00A0 Right now it\u0027s just the accent lines here and there.\u00A0 More decals would be neat. Maybe this could be a good mod idea.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T08:19:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677042249\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225367\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Astr0Guy5\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Astr0Guy5 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfeature added later in development (confirmed by Lowne I think?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe talked about a color pipette coming in the future.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}